title: Manhattan's Tightening East Side Office Market
text:
Manhattan’s Tightening East Side Office Market Once relatively cheap, space is filling up fast By Keiko.Morris@wsj.com Aug. 2, 2015 8:54 p.m. ET 
Office space on Manhattan’s East Side, long one of Midtown’s less-expensive destinations, is filling up fast. 
The East Side’s availability rate—the percentage of office space that is vacant or will become available in the next 12 months—hit 4.9% in June, making it the tightest of all Midtown submarkets, according to CBRE Group Inc.’s research group.
